   = HTML is HyperText Markup Language, it allows us to structure our web d
    = HTML consists of a series of elements which there are two type:
      = element which use to wrap some text and consist of opening tag and an end tag.
       
            <p>This is paragraph element</p>
    
    = Tags are element's name surrounded by angle bracket
      = HTML tags can also have attributes

            <a href="www.google.com">this link naviagate to google</a>
      
      = the 'href' is tag's attribute.
      = element which doesn't have a closing tag as it doesn't wrap anything.

            <img src="/folder/to/your/image.jpg" />
    
